  "title": "Test plot size in pigeonpea",
  "abstract": "It is important for. breeders and agronomists  , to know what plot size is adequate for corir ducting their trials.    In pigeonpeas., information on plot size is scanty.   Therefore, a preliminary investigation was carried out by harvesting individual rows from six-row plots in a replicated yield trial.",
